title: Bill Caswell
description: Matt returns from Europe and Bill Caswell joins us to talk about the Volvo S60 Polestar, electric hot-rodding, the Fiesta ST, partying at the Nurburging, rally built 911s, and driving in the UK in a Morgan Aero 8.
author: matt@thesmokingtire.com (Matt Farah & Zack Klapman)
